text: Locate the structure that is rectangular in shape, has a dark roof with lighter spots, and features uniformly spaced square elements along one side.
Find the building characterized by a large rectangular form, a dark roof interspersed with lighter areas, and square features that are evenly distributed along one edge.
Spot the edifice with a substantial rectangular outline, a dark rooftop marked by lighter patches, and square features evenly placed along a single side.
